{"tid":848382,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix落實重製《魔幻王國》系列","createTime":"2018-10-05T01:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T07:11:00.000Z","uid":6604,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"82218db1db998ea82802eafa66b490494cbaabb4","tid":848382,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T01:16:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181005/58756644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58756644&d=hHJgFXFQMACfCY1nZCs3oE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4510ffcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58756644&h=54b1eafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181005/58756644</a><br />\n<br />\n改編自同名小說，曾被製作成同名電影嘅《魔幻王國》系列，將會由串流電視台Netflix重製成電影。呢本童話小說於1950年寫成，曾被多次改編，最近一次為2005年改編成電影《魔幻王國：獅子．女巫．魔衣櫥》（The Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe），其後亦有續集。現時仲未知Netflix會拍成幾多部電影，監製Mark Gordon就指一定唔止一部，更有可能同時有戲又有劇。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9ada7b3cb0c778af309e3d41347bd250e243f7","tid":848382,"uid":34572,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:46:08.000Z","msg":"其實當時黎明行者號又唔係唔收得，點解唔再拍落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電影嚟講我其實鍾意納尼亞系列多過哈利波特"},{"pid":"55debe70d42dedeb90835ac400cd04fc8b064d02","tid":848382,"uid":93784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018